l</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">灵活简单的标签特性</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">每周更新一个新功能</p></li></ul><h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 30px; font-family: Helvetica, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 36px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: text; position: relative;\"><a class=\"anchor\" id=\"安全性\" href=\"https://git.oschina.net/houdunwang/hdcms#安全性\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: -25px; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); text-decoration: none; display: block; cursor: pointer; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\"></a>安全性</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22px;\">HDCMS完全基于后盾网HDPHP框架开发提供了众多的安全特性，产品安全无忧。这些特性包括：</p><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22px;\"><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">COOKIE加密处理</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">数据预处理机制</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">XSS安全防护</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">表单自动验证</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">强制数据类型转换</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">输入数据过滤</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">表单令牌验证</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">防SQL注入</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">图像上传检测</p></li></ul><h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 30px; font-family: Helvetica, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 36px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); white-space: normal; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; cursor: text; position: relative;\"><a class=\"anchor\" id=\"商业友好的开源协议\" href=\"https://git.oschina.net/houdunwang/hdcms#商业友好的开源协议\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: -25px; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); text-decoration: none; display: block; cursor: pointer; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\"></a>商业友好的开源协议</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Helvetica, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22px;\">HDCMS遵循Apache2开源协议发布。Apache Licence是著名的非盈利开源组织Apache采用的协议。该协议和BSD类似，鼓励代码共享和尊重原作者的著作权，同样允许代码修改，再作为开源或商业软件发布。</p><p><br/></p>')");
$db->exe("REPLACE INTO ".$db_prefix."content_data (`aid`,`content`) VALUES('2','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">后盾网做为国内知名的PHP培训机构有以下几个特点：</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://localhost/hdcms/upload/content/2014/05/08/59211399554645.jpg\" title=\"231643jccfzv3izucfk2am.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">1 起步最晚，发展最快的PHP培训机构</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">2 唯一拥有众多PHP开源产品的培训机构</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">3 唯一有能力开发PHP框架的培训机构</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">4 唯一有能力开发高效HDCMS的培训机构</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">5 唯一有能力发布高质量VIP实战视频教程的培训机构</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">6 唯一以实战贯穿培训始终的PHP培训机构</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">7 唯一有培训PHP底层框架开发的培训机构(不是单纯用框架，而是让每名学员独立写出自己的框架）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">8 只有后盾网的学员能独立开发实战项目，不分组（大部分培训机构以分组形式开发项目，因为学员一个人没有能力与时间完成，在后盾网不存在这样的问题）</p><p><br/></p>')");
